
Docker registry

1.In this lab, we will explore some concepts related to Docker Registry and also practice setting up our own simple registry server.

2.What is a Docker Registry?

3.By default, the Docker engine interacts with?

By default, the Docker Engine interacts with Docker Hub as its default Docker registry.
So, when you run:
docker pull nginx
Docker actually pulls the image from Docker Hub unless another registry is specified.

