10.Now, we can pull images from our registry-server as well. Use docker pull [server-addr/image-name] to pull the images that we pushed earlier.
In our case, we can use:
docker pull localhost:5000/nginx

11.Finally, let's clean up our registry.
Stop and remove the my-registry container.

Run the following command first:
docker container stop my-registry
 And then:
docker container rm my-registry

